---
title: Beef and Pineapple Fried Rice with Hoisin-Soy Drizzle
description: Chunks of juicy pineapple give ordinary fried rice a sweet-savoury appeal that's hard to resist. All that's missing from this delicious Thai-inspired dish is the whole pineapple to serve it in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-pineapple-fried-rice-391cd0b3.jpg
